   |-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
hal: hal (Hardware abstraction layer daemon)
hal:
hal: HAL is a hardware abstraction layer for GNU/Linux, designed to help
hal: make hardware "just work".
hal:
hal: !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
hal: IMPORTANT NOTE:
hal: !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
hal:
hal: To make hardware "just work" for non-root users as well, you must
hal: add these users to the "halusers" group (group id "62" by default)!
